display="block">         \operatorname {H}^\bullet (X,G;F)         \xrightarrow {\sim } \operatorname {H}^\bullet (X\times  U_G,G;\operatorname {pr}_1^*F)         \xleftarrow {\sim } \operatorname {H}^\bullet (X\times  U_G/G,F^G).       \tag{6.1.4.1}       </fr:tex></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter><fr:contributions></fr:contributions><fr:context><fr:tree
